<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dashboard - EmpowerFund</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    /* Reset and global styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #fff;
      color: #333;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Header styling */
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Navigation styling */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    nav a:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Section styling */
    .section {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .section:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }

    .section ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .section ul li {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .section ul li:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
      transform: translateX(10px);
    }

    .section ul li strong {
      color: #6a11cb;
    }

    /* Flash messages styling */
    .alert {
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .alert-error {
      background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
      color: #ff6b6b;
    }

    .alert-success {
      background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
      color: #66ff66;
    }

    /* Footer styling */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    footer p {
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to EmpowerFund, <%= user.name %>!</h1>
    <p>Your one-stop solution for financial growth and wealth management.</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="/dashboard">Home</a>
    <a href="/sip">SIP Calculator</a>
    <a href="/emi">EMI Calculator</a>
    <a href="/investments">Investment Options</a>
    <a href="/stocks">Stock Market Data</a>
    <a href="">Educational resources</a>
    <a href="">financial planning</a>
    <a href="">Tools for Budgeting</a>
    <a href="/api/users/logout">Logout</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Display flash messages (if any) -->
  <% if (messages.error) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-error">
      <%= messages.error %>
    </div>
  <% } %>
  <% if (messages.success) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-success">
      <%= messages.success %>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="section">
    <p>Explore the tools and resources available to you. Whether you're planning for retirement, saving for a big purchase, or investing in the stock market, EmpowerFund provides you with the tools and insights to make informed financial decisions.</p>
    <p>Our platform offers:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>SIP Calculator:</strong> Plan your Systematic Investment Plans with precision.</li>
      <li><strong>EMI Calculator:</strong> Calculate your Equated Monthly Installments for loans.</li>
      <li><strong>Investment Options:</strong> Discover a variety of investment opportunities tailored to your goals.</li>
      <li><strong>Stock Market Data:</strong> Stay updated with real-time stock market trends and analysis.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 EmpowerFund. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>